article_title: Man Stabbed At OKC Bar; Police Looking For Second Victim - News9.com - Oklahoma City, OK - News, Weather, Video and Sports
article_text:
The attack was reported just after 2:30 a.m. at the El Divorcio Bar in the 2500 block of S. Robinson in S.W. Oklahoma City.

A man was stabbed at a bar early Monday morning and police say there may be a second victim.

The attack was reported just after 2:30 a.m. at the El Divorcio Bar in the 2500 block of S. Robinson in S.W. Oklahoma City.

At least one man is in the hospital.



Police said they were looking for a possible second victim involved in the incident.

No other details have been released at this time.
